r\n\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;CENTER&quot; class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal&quot;&gt;E-Commerce assignment 2013&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;CENTER&quot; class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal&quot;&gt;Philip Afful Nunoo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;CENTER&quot; class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal&quot;&gt;Kwame Nkrumah University of Science and Technology&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;CENTER&quot; class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal&quot;&gt;Department of Computer science&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;CENTER&quot; class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal&quot;&gt;5085410&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;CENTER&quot; class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;4&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16pt&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Web Server?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;CENTER&quot; class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Web server&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt; can refer to either the hardware (the computer) or the software (the computer application) that helps to deliver Web content that can be accessed through the Internet or a network.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 13pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;What is used for?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;Overview&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;The primary function of a web server is to deliver web pages on the request to clients using the Hypertext Transfer Protocol (HTTP). &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Many generic web servers also support server-side scripting using Active Server Pages (ASP), PHP, or other scripting languages.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 13pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Examples of web servers?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.89in; margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Apache&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt; by Apache&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.89in; margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;IIS (Internet Information Service) &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;by Microsoft&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.89in; margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;nginx &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;by NGINX, Inc&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.89in; margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;GWS &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;by Google&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 13pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;How to setup a personal web server? (Using Apache on Linux)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;What is Apacehe?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Apache is one of the most popular web servers, and it&amp;#39;s also free. It also has a lot of features that make it very extensible and useful for many different types of websites. It is a server that is used for everything from personal web pages to enterprise level sites.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Apache can be set up in almost every Operating System Easily by the use of solution stacks eg. LAMP, WAMP, etc.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Setting up Apache on Linux&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 13pt&quot;&gt;Installing Apache&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Apache can be obtained and installed using the linux package installer&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;We have to get Apache working now.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Open up the Terminal (Applications &amp;gt; Accessories &amp;gt; Terminal). &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol start=&quot;2&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Copy/Paste or type the following line of code.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0.2in&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;sudo apt-get install apache2&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol start=&quot;3&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;The terminal will ask you for a password ie your root password enter and continue.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;4&quot;&gt;Testing Apache&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;To make sure everything installed correctly we will now test Apache to ensure it is working properly.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Open up any web browser and then enter the following into the web address:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0.2in&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;http://localhost/&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;You should see a folder entitled apache2-default/. Open it and you will see a message saying &amp;quot;It works!&amp;quot; , congrats to you! or something like that!&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Installing a scripting language (PHP) to work with apache.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;4&quot;&gt;Installing PHP&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;We will now install PHP 5 .&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Open up the terminal &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol start=&quot;2&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Enter the following code&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0.2in&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;sudo apt-get install php5 libapache2-mod-php5&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol start=&quot;3&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;We now restart our Apache server to work with php. To restart apache you enter&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0.2in&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 restart&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;4&quot;&gt;Testing Your PHP&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Now lets see whether our php is functioning on apache.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;We create a file to test our php. Create a file (eg. test.php) and place in the /var/www folder&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0.2in&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;sudo gedit /var/www/test.php&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol start=&quot;2&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Copy and paste line below into the file.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0.2in&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;lt;?php phpinfo(); ?&amp;gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol start=&quot;3&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Save and close the file.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol start=&quot;4&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Open your browser and enter the following. http://localhost/test.php&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;(It will show you the page that has all information about your php. If you have prior experience of installing php in some other OS, you must have seen this page.)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Congrats we have now installed both Apache and PHP!&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Installing a Database (MySQL) to work with apache and PHP&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;4&quot;&gt;Install MySQL&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;We now install our sql database server.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Once again open the terminal and enter&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0.2in&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;sudo apt-get install mysql-server&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol start=&quot;2&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;(optional) in order for order computers to view your server, we must edit the &amp;quot;Blind Address&amp;quot;. ie. 127.0.0.1&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0.2in&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;gksudo gedit /etc/mysql/my.cnf&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol start=&quot;3&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n	&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Change the line&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0.2in&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;bind-address = 127.0.0.1&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Change the address(127.0.0.1) to your IP address.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;If it so happens you weren&amp;#39;t asked to provide a root password you would have to do so manually to do so, from your terminal enter.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;~/ mysql -u root&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;mysql&amp;gt; SET PASSWORD FOR &amp;#39;root&amp;#39;@&amp;#39;localhost&amp;#39; = PASSWORD(&amp;#39;yourpassword&amp;#39;)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;make sure you insert your password at &amp;quot;yourpassword&amp;quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;We are now going to install a program called phpMyAdmin which would help up edit our databases.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.49in; margin-bottom: 0.2in&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;sudo apt-get install libapache2-mod-auth-mysql php5-mysql phpmyadmin&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Now we try to also make PHP work with MySQL. To do this we will need to open a file entitled php.ini.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 1.02in; margin-bottom: 0.2in&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;gksudo gedit /etc/php5/apache2/php.ini&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Now uncomment the following lines of code by taking out the semicolons(;).&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 1in; margin-bottom: 0.2in&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;;extension=mysql.so&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;Now restart apache again for the new configuration to take effect.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;pre class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0.97in; margin-bottom: 0.2in&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 restart&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '2013-03-21', '2013-03-21', 0),
(13, 1, 'Here', '&lt;p&gt;Document is here&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '2013-03-31', '2013-03-31', 0);

